WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:31.498 --> 00:00:34.384
Hello everyone! We are now in Shiding!!

00:00:34.384 --> 00:00:37.070
Today we are going to take the second section of Taipei Skyline

00:00:37.070 --> 00:00:39.155
... Later we will take the route

00:00:39.155 --> 00:00:41.658
from the West Peak to the Emperor's Hall and the Emperor's

00:00:41.658 --> 00:00:43.359
Hall!! We are now going to take

00:01:10.403 --> 00:01:12.305
the route from the West Peak to the Emperor's Hall

00:01:12.305 --> 00:01:14.474
... Go up and dig

00:01:40.800 --> 00:01:41.584
that house forest...

00:01:41.584 --> 00:01:42.669
Acudu, two cans of biluji grains,

00:01:42.969 --> 00:01:44.053
braised eggs

00:01:44.053 --> 00:01:45.138
and two kelp!!

00:01:55.198 --> 00:01:55.765
Oh!!

00:01:56.716 --> 00:01:57.817
Now on the west peak...

00:01:58.818 --> 00:02:00.503
the last section has added...

00:02:01.437 --> 00:02:02.155
handrails!!

00:02:03.289 --> 00:02:04.457
better than before There are a lot of things

00:02:06.626 --> 00:02:07.677
I was here last time... I slid a little bit in the

00:02:08.361 --> 00:02:09.896
last night.

00:07:41.611 --> 00:07:42.612
We just

00:07:43.529 --> 00:07:45.281
came down from the east peak of the Emperor's Palace!! Now I'm going back to Shixing Old Street.

00:07:45.281 --> 00:07:47.333
I'm ready to go back now. Go to Shiding Old Street ~

00:07:48.117 --> 00:07:49.852
The weather is too hot today

00:07:50.736 --> 00:07:52.905
...

00:07:54.090 --> 00:07:55.942
Just walk along the east and west peaks of the Emperor's Palace!!

00:08:14.093 --> 00:08:15.912
There are check-in points here...

00:08:19.115 --> 00:08:21.434
Many people go up here. Now when you come down from

00:08:30.860 --> 00:08:32.695
the east peak, there are drink stalls

00:08:33.095 --> 00:08:34.947
here. , there are still things to eat!!

00:08:34.947 --> 00:08:36.632
(OK!! Thank you!!)

00:08:36.632 --> 00:08:39.135
There are two companies selling cold drinks

00:08:39.986 --> 00:08:41.404
and there are toilets for washing!!

00:08:42.638 --> 00:08:46.642
Our toilet is fifty or sixty... fifty or sixty years old!!

00:08:48.177 --> 00:08:49.845
My husband's Dad's

00:08:49.845 --> 00:08:52.665
toilet... Auntie said that their house is being cleaned and then

00:08:52.848 --> 00:08:54.166
built with rough stones

00:08:55.668 --> 00:08:57.336
from his father-in-law

00:08:58.037 --> 00:08:59.906
, so... when you come here,

00:08:59.989 --> 00:09:01.240
you can buy their drinks

00:09:02.058 --> 00:09:02.875
(thank you!)

00:09:02.925 --> 00:09:03.960
and tell them!!

00:09:05.144 --> 00:09:08.180
They are the aborigines. Their own private land (donated)

00:09:08.531 --> 00:09:12.535
is open for everyone to use.

00:09:19.942 --> 00:09:21.527
We are now coming out from...

00:09:21.727 --> 00:09:24.730
the small rough pit archway on the east peak of the Yellow Emperor's Palace!!

00:09:25.448 --> 00:09:27.516
Today, the Emperor's Palace...

00:09:27.950 --> 00:09:29.352
walks against the East and West Peaks!!

00:09:30.052 --> 00:09:30.486
We have finished...

00:09:30.486 --> 00:09:31.988
.We will go to Shiding Old Street to eat later .

